<para style="q1">

<verse number="14" style="v" />The wicked have drawn out their swords and have bent their bows</para>

<para style="q1">to cast down the oppressed and needy,</para>

<para style="q1">to kill those who are upright.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="15" style="v" />Their swords will pierce their own hearts,</para>

<para style="q1">and their bows will be broken.</para>
